Girl, Interrupted;;84;;53;;R;;Set in the changing world of the late 1960s, "Girl, Interrupted" is the searing true story of Susanna Kaysen (Winona Ryder), a young woman who finds herself at a renowned mental institution for troubled young women, where she must choose between the world of people who belong on the inside -- like the seductive and dangerous Lisa (Angelina Jolie) -- or the often difficult world of reality on the outside.;;Drama;;James Mangold;;1999;;Winona Ryder,Angelina Jolie,Clea Duvall,Brittany Murphy,Elisabeth Moss,Jared Leto,Jeffrey Tambor,Vanessa Redgrave,Whoopi Goldberg,Mary Kay Place,Jillian Armenante,Steve Altes,Angela Bettis,John Bobby,Travis Fine;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/girl_interrupted